response.overview: On September 17th GCW faces off TNT live on FITE straight from Hangar 34 in Liverpool, UK. The lineup has well over 7 matches and you can check all of them below:  Joey Janela vs Gene Munny  Effy vs Che Monet  Tony Deppen vs Man Like DeReiss  Tag Team Match  Jordan Oliver & Nick Wayne vs Kings Of The North (Bonesaw & Damien Corvin)  Allie Katch vs Lizzy Evo  Robbie X vs Blake Christian  Six Man Tag Team Death Match  Big Joe, Clint Margera & Drew Parker vs Alex Colon, Jimmy Lloyd & John Wayne Murdoch
response.title: GCW vs TNT
